# RPGer Backend Environment Variables

# OpenRouter API Key
# Get your API key from https://openrouter.ai/
# This key is required for the AI capabilities of the RPGer application
# The key should start with "sk-" followed by a string of characters
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=your_api_key_here

# Model Configuration
# The following models are available through OpenRouter:
# - mistralai/mistral-7b-instruct (Tier 1, default)
# - anthropic/claude-instant-1.2 (Tier 2)
# - anthropic/claude-3-haiku-20240307 (Tier 3)
#
# The application will automatically use the appropriate model based on the complexity of the task.
# No configuration is needed for this, but you can modify the model tiers in openrouter_agent_manager.py if desired.

# Other configuration settings can be added here
